The dynamic response of the confined water layer was phenomenologically described by a second-order system for a damped oscillator,5md2ydt2+sgndydt⋅CDρAsdydt2=mg−ρgV(y)\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
				\usepackage{amssymb}
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
